com.Comphenix.PacketWrapper

类 WrapperPlayServerCollect

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.Comphenix.PacketWrapper.AbstractPacket
      • com.Comphenix.PacketWrapper.WrapperPlayServerCollect

  • public class WrapperPlayServerCollect
extends AbstractPacket
    Sent by the server when an iten stack is collected from the ground. This packet simply initiates the collect item animation, nothing more.

    Kristian
